OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,F's Environment & Infrastructure
OL,7,FCommittee has published a new strategy
OL,8,Fto improve to the island's road
OL,9,Fnetwork.
OL,11,FPart of the "Better Transport Plan"
OL,12,Fexplores how to better connect new and
OL,13,Fexisting roads with several new
OL,14,Fhousing developments.
