OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,FDeputy Adrian Gabriel, Vice President
OL,7,Ffor Environment & Infrastructure said:
OL,8,F"We know there's going to be about a
OL,9,Fthousand houses delivered in the North
OL,10,Fof the island on various sites and
OL,11,Fthis better transport project is about
OL,12,Fconnecting those sites together with
OL,13,Fstate funded initiatives."
OL,15,FMore than 1000 new homes are expected
OL,16,Fto be built across sites such as; the
OL,17,FFontaine Vinery, Les Bas Courtils,
OL,18,FPointes Rocques, Franc Fief, Saltpans
OL,19,FKey Industrial Estate Area, Cleveleys
OL,20,FVinery, Saltpans and Leale's Yard.
