OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, President
OL,7,Fof E&I added: "Our road infrastructure
OL,8,Fis already not serving residents in
OL,9,Fthe north anywhere near as well as it
OL,10,Fcould.
OL,12,F"This Plan will guide improvements to
OL,13,Ftransport options as those
OL,14,Fdevelopments move forward.
