OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,F"We want to be proactive in our
OL,7,Fefforts to minimise any negative
OL,8,Fimpacts of likely new development and
OL,9,Fuse the opportunity to create in the
OL,10,Fprocess some additional benefits for
OL,11,Fthe current and future residents
OL,12,Falike."
OL,14,FThe committee says that this plan will
OL,15,F"pave the way for a wider and better
OL,16,Frange of transport choices" with the
OL,17,Fhope that more islanders will choose
OL,18,Fto use buses, bikes and travel by foot.
