OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez said:
OL,7,F"This is not going to be a magic wand
OL,8,Fsolution, it's not going to be
OL,9,Fsomething that comes in overnight.
OL,11,F"It is going to be implemented in a
OL,12,Fnumber of different ways over a number
OL,13,Fof different years."
OL,15,FPeople living in the area covered by
OL,16,Fthe Better Transport Plan should
OL,17,Freceive a detailed letter shortly.
